    "title": "iHealth OpenAPI v2",
    "version": "2.0",
    "description": "iHealth Labs OpenAPI v2 provides access to health data from iHealth connected devices including blood pressure monitors, glucometers, pulse oximeters, weight scales, activity trackers, and body composition analyzers. Uses OAuth2 for authorization.",
